{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/smartwatch-masihkah-mereka-relevan-untuk-dibeli/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Smartwatch: Masihkah Mereka Relevan Untuk Dibeli?","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Saya cukup yakin kalau ada diantara bro sis sekalian ada yang memiliki dan menggunakan smartwatch dalam kegiatan sehari-hari. Entah itu untuk platform iOS ataupun Android. Normalnya penggunaan smartwatch mengharuskan proses pairing dengan smartphone yang sesuai sebelum bisa mulai digunakan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pemakaian dan kegunaan smartwatch juga tergantung kecanggihan teknologi yang dia usung. Secara otomatis dan <em>default</em>, sebuah smartwatch melakukan hal-hal yang juga dilakukan oleh smartphone, dalam versi yang lebih sederhana tentunya. Ini termasuk membaca pesan teks, melihat jadwal, sampai menjawab panggilan telepon. Semua hal, termasuk tentunya hal dasar dari sebuah jam tangan seperti menunjukkan waktu, dapat dilakukan pemakai smartwatch melalui pergelangan tangannya. Sangat memudahkan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42269\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42269\" data-attachment-id=\"42269\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Ex-President Obama juga pernah menggunakan smartwatch Fitbit. Sumber gambar: qrcodepress.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ex-President Obama juga pernah menggunakan smartwatch Fitbit. Sumber gambar: qrcodepress.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42269\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-5.jpg\" alt=\"Ex-President Obama juga pernah menggunakan smartwatch Fitbit. Sumber gambar: qrcodepress.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42269\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ex-President Obama juga pernah menggunakan smartwatch Fitbit. Sumber gambar: qrcodepress.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebuah smartwatch biasanya akan memiliki layar berteknologi tinggi dengan jenis layar <em>backlit</em> LCD atau OLED. Tak hanya layar keren, sebuah smartwatch juga dibarengi hal-hal lain yang berguna seperti layar sentuh, baterai rechargable, thermometer, accelerometer, pedometer (pengukur jarak dan jumlah langkah kaki), pengukur detak jantung, kompas, altimeter, sampai GPS untuk penanda peta. Benda sekecil itu dijejali berbagai hal dan teknologi sehingga menyandang gelar “smart” yang menunjukkan kepintarannya dalam melakukan banyak hal.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42278\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42278\" data-attachment-id=\"42278\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Disebut jam pintar karena memang pintar. Sumber gambar: digitaltrends.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Disebut jam pintar karena memang pintar. Sumber gambar: digitaltrends.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42278\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-3.jpg\" alt=\"Disebut jam pintar karena memang pintar. Sumber gambar: digitaltrends.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42278\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Disebut jam pintar karena memang pintar. Sumber gambar: digitaltrends.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi sebenarnya kapan smartwatch ini mulai dikenal luas?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kalau mau ditarik mulai dari sejarah awal jam tangan digital, itu terjadi tahun 1972 dengan lahirnya “Pulsar” dari perusahaan jam tangan Swiss, Hamilton Watch Company.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42268\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42268\" data-attachment-id=\"42268\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jam tangan digital pertama di dunia. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jam tangan digital pertama di dunia. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42268\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-4.jpg\" alt=\"Jam tangan digital pertama di dunia. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42268\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jam tangan digital pertama di dunia. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Samsung membuat ‘jam telepon pertama di dunia’ tahun 1999 yang bernama SPH-WP10. Jam ini punya antena yang bisa ditarik memanjang, layar monokrom jenis LCD dan kemampuan bertelepon melalui mic dan speaker onboard-nya selama 90 menit. Pada masa itu tentunya ini sebuah kecanggihan teknologi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42274\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42274\" data-attachment-id=\"42274\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Benda ini berfungsi sebagai telepon juga. Sumber gambar: tecmundo.com.brBenda ini berfungsi sebagai telepon juga. Sumber gambar: tecmundo.com.br\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Benda ini berfungsi sebagai telepon juga. Sumber gambar: tecmundo.com.br&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42274\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-1.jpg\" alt=\"Benda ini berfungsi sebagai telepon juga. Sumber gambar: tecmundo.com.br\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42274\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Benda ini berfungsi sebagai telepon juga. Sumber gambar: tecmundo.com.br</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tahun 2013 lahir tiga jenis smartwatch yang cukup berpengaruh dan jadi berita penting saat itu yakni Samsung Galaxy Gear, Sony Smartwatch 2 dan Qualcomm Toq. Saat itu Android menjadi pilihan sistem operasi smartwatch dunia. Pilihan yang tepat karena era smartphone yang di dominasi oleh Android sehingga merupakan langkah strategis untuk menggunakan Android di smartwatch yang di-pairing dengan smartphone.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42273\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42273\" data-attachment-id=\"42273\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sony Smartwatch 2. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sony Smartwatch 2. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42273\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch.jpg\" alt=\"Sony Smartwatch 2. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42273\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sony Smartwatch 2. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apakah Apple dengan iOS nya tidak ikutan cari untung di pasar smartwatch?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Walau telat datang ke pesta, namun Apple juga ikut meramaikan pasar smartwatch dunia. Mereka meluncurkan Apple Watch tahun 2015. Smartwatch mereka panen kritikan saat diluncurkan, terutama di bagian daya tahan baterai dan malfungsi perangkat yang mengganggu. Namun fans Apple yang terkenal loyal [<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-fans-apple-sangat-loyal/\">Alasan Mengapa Fans Apple  Sangat Loyal?</a>] tetap berjubel memenuhi Apple Store dan membeli satu. Salah satu argumen mereka adalah Apple Watch bahkan bisa menandingi ekslusivitas jam tangah fashion keluaran brand-brand pembuat jam tangan seperti Seiko, Swatch, Emporio Armani, Tag Heuer, AP dan lainnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42277\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42277\" data-attachment-id=\"42277\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Saya fans Apple tapi menurut saya desain Apple Watch tidak menarik. Sumber gambar: apple.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Saya fans Apple tapi menurut saya desain Apple Watch tidak menarik. Sumber gambar: apple.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42277\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-8.jpg\" alt=\"Saya fans Apple tapi menurut saya desain Apple Watch tidak menarik. Sumber gambar: apple.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42277\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Saya fans Apple tapi menurut saya desain Apple Watch tidak menarik. Sumber gambar: apple.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi sepertinya smartwatch mulai mengalami ‘seleksi alam’.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pabrikan teknologi seperti Pebble, Motorola dan bahkan Microsoft sudah menyatakan kalau mereka pensiun dari kompetisi pembuatan “wearable smart device” seperti smartwatch. Asus sedang mempertimbangkan diri untuk ikutan mundur dari persaingan dan hal ini jadi meninggalkan sedikit pemain smartwatch yang tersisa.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apple Watch Series 3, Samsung Gear Sport, Fitbit Ionic dan Garmin Vivoactive 3 adalah sedikit dari yang tersisa itu.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keempatnya memiliki fitur yang nyaris sama dan serupa seperti built-in GPS, sensor detak jantung, kemampuan streaming musik (kecuali Garmin), NFC untuk pembayaran sistem elektronik, tahan air hingga kedalaman 50 meter dan bahkan harga yang seragam di US$ 300 (kecuali Apple, yang pede menjual Apple Watch mereka di harga US$ 329).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Masihkah mereka relevan untuk dibeli saat ini?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tentu saja tergantung kebutuhan dan budget di tangan. Jika bro sis pemakai iPhone, memiliki Apple Watch akan menjadi nilai tambah. Tidak hanya karena “cocok berpasangan dengan iPhone”, Apple Watch akan memudahkan pendataan kesehatan, kompatiblitas dengan Apple Pay (layanan NFC payment Apple) maupun streaming musik lewat Apple Music.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42279\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42279\" data-attachment-id=\"42279\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Apple Watch 3 masih mengusung desain yang tidak seksi. Sumber gambar: apple.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Apple Watch 3 masih mengusung desain yang tidak seksi. Sumber gambar: apple.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42279\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-9.jpg\" alt=\"Apple Watch 3 masih mengusung desain yang tidak seksi. Sumber gambar: apple.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42279\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Apple Watch 3 masih mengusung desain yang tidak seksi. Sumber gambar: apple.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sementara Samsung Gear Sport menggunaka OS Tizen made-in Samsung sendiri dan dirancang tangguh untuk kegiatan outdoor seperti menyelam.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42276\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42276\" data-attachment-id=\"42276\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain menarik mirip jam tangan konvensional. Sumber gambar: theverge.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Desain menarik mirip jam tangan konvensional. Sumber gambar: theverge.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42276\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-2.jpg\" alt=\"Desain menarik mirip jam tangan konvensional. Sumber gambar: theverge.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42276\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain menarik mirip jam tangan konvensional. Sumber gambar: theverge.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fitbit Ionic membanggakan daya tahan baterai mereka yang hingga 5 hari, walau itu masih belum se-impresif Garmin Vivoactive 3 yang baterainya bisa <em>standby</em> sampai 7 hari per sekali charge.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42275\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42275\" data-attachment-id=\"42275\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/smartwatch-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fitbit Ionic. Sumber gambar: brookstone.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fitbit Ionic. Sumber gambar: brookstone.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42275\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-7.jpg\" alt=\"Fitbit Ionic. Sumber gambar: brookstone.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/smartwatch-7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p